
/*
Configure build with [tsconfig.json]

step 1: define a tsconfig file on root [tsc -init]
step 3: got to tsconfig.json and then delete all code and add this code bellow:
{
 "compilerOptions": {
  "outDir": "dist"
 },
 "include": ["./src/**/*"],
// }

/*
step 3: run TSC on root [tsc]
step 4: run node on dist folder [node dist/Main.js]




while developin you can also use ts-node configure your code

step 1: install ts-node (if not done yet)
    npm install -g ts-node

step 2: check your package is installed 
    npm list -g

step 2: run ts-node on root
    ts-node src/Main.ts



